Schema Definitions

L2VPN-EVPN-EVI-DETAIL:

EVPN E-VPN ID database detail information

rd-configured: L2VPN-RD

Configured Route Distinguisher

aliasing-disabled: boolean

Route Aliasing is disabled

multicast-label: integer

Multicast Label

bd-name: string

Bridge domain name

unknown-unicast-flooding-disabled: boolean

Unknown-unicast flooding is disabled

cw-disable: boolean

Control-Word Disable

forward-class: integer

Forward Class attribute

evpn-instance: L2VPN-EVPN-EVI-SUMMARY

EVPN Instance summary information

rt-auto: L2VPN-RT

Automatic Route Target

reoriginate-disabled: boolean

Route Re-origination is disabled

advertise-bvi-mac: boolean

Advertise BVI MACs routes on this EVI

type: string evpn-type-invalid, evpn-type-evpn, evpn-type-pbb-evpn, evpn-type-evpn-vpws-vlan-unaware, evpn-type-evpn-vpws-vlan-aware, evpn-type-max

Service Type

table-policy-name: string

Table-policy Name

encapsulation-xr: integer

EVPN Instance encapsulation

description: string

EVI description

unicast-label: integer

Unicast Label

advertise-mac: boolean

Advertise MAC-only routes on this EVI

rd-auto: L2VPN-RD

Automatic Route Distingtuisher

stitching: boolean

EVPN Instance is Regular/Stitching side

rt-export-block-set: boolean

Is Export RT None set

rt-import-block-set: boolean

Is Import RT None set

flow-label: L2VPN-EVPN-FLOW-LABEL

Flow Label Information

evi-xr: integer

E-VPN id

L2VPN-TDM:

L2VPN TDM parameters

tdm-mode: string unknown, ce-so-psn, sa-to-p-e1, sa-to-p-t1, sa-to-p-e3, sa-to-p-t3

TDM mode

timeslot-rate: integer

Timeslot rate in units of Kbps

tdm-options: L2VPN-TDM-OPTION

TDM options

timeslot-group: string

Timeslots separated by , or - from 1 to 31. : indicates individual timeslot and - represents a range.E.g. 1-3,5 represents timeslots 1, 2, 3, and 5.

Example
{
  "tdm-mode": "string",
  "timeslot-rate": "integer",
  "tdm-options": {

    "ssrc": "integer",

    "payload-bytes": "integer",

    "timestamp-clock-freq": "integer",
    "cas": "integer",
    "rtp": "string"
  },
  "timeslot-group": "string"
}

rtp-header-payload-type: integer

RTP header payload type

bit-rate: integer

TDM bit rate in units of Kbps

payload-bytes: integer

TDM payload bytes

timestamp-mode: string unknown, differential, absolute, none

TDM Timestamping mode

timestamp-clock-freq: integer

Timestamping clock frequency in units of 8Khz

cas: integer

CAS

rtp: string unknown, present, absent

RTP header

Example
{
  "signalling-packets": "integer",

  "payload-bytes": "integer",

  "timestamp-clock-freq": "integer",
  "cas": "integer",
  "rtp": "string"
